{"tid":1481621,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"革命成功與否 我地都要支持其他國家爭取民主","createTime":"2019-08-17T18:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T14:33:57.000Z","uid":20584,"like":93,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"864974bc5eed7360eb8bc5f5403ddee4e4780a15","tid":1481621,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:47:34.000Z","msg":"見到文宣片幾十個國家幾十種語言話支持香港  我好感動 <br />\n<br />\n應承我 即使今次成功與否，他日邊個國家需要我地聲援 我地都要幫！ 咁先顯得出我地香港人質素！<br />\n<br />\n諗返起法國黃背心革命 台灣茉莉花革命開始左個陣 香港人都係當普通新聞咁睇 不了了之 <br />\n<br />\n而今次 全世界都幫緊我地 我地唔可以忘記依份恩情！ 有恩必報啊"},{"pid":"484939b2b7529122a02c8ee3d7120c015071e102","tid":1481621,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:47:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8b72e5222212799218ab20b53621aa151c8d0202","tid":1481621,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:48:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1eb9710f49582f83764e3ebb55ef209e7da7c341","tid":1481621,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:49:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1fde46d8fcac6b57bf3e64321d92779d9d9c9918","tid":1481621,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:49:46.000Z","msg":"報恩啊！"},{"pid":"451b70730bbef5b3c04d44f5b7b7303495525c8f","tid":1481621,"uid":277873,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:49:57.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n一直有關注外地民主運動，希望經過這些事後香港人對國際政治能有更多感同身受的關注"},{"pid":"1039c5c67b326e93ae42953088689274ead9b173","tid":1481621,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:50:25.000Z","msg":"聽日衝衝既勇武派 睇睇郭文貴呢段片先<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.guo.media/broadcasts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guo.media%2Fbroadcasts&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1JLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=219282e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.guo.media/broadcasts</a><br />\n2:00：00開始睇<br />\n千其咪衝<br />\n唔好掉入 香港700萬 對14 億既陷阱<br />\n中共想你地敵對<br />\n根本垃圾魔鬼黎<br />\n你地鬥完 就唔會燒到共產黨<br />\n狠毒到仆街既共狗黨"},{"pid":"c609cefa67e34db467d1a29e07db6e30842fca97","tid":1481621,"uid":296565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:51:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7f43ca152f9a9db3529478be85cb15e85dbccb1","tid":1481621,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:51:23.000Z","msg":"報恩!報恩!"},{"pid":"b88beae3fca77a7dc586de1565f6d1a5e0beff09","tid":1481621,"uid":20584,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"451b70730bbef5b3c04d44f5b7b7303495525c8f","tid":1481621,"uid":277873,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:49:57.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n一直有關注外地民主運動，希望經過這些事後香港人對國際政治能有更多感同身受的關注"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:51:24.000Z","msg":"係真 人地唔係老奉幫你 希望香港人唔好之後只顧自己 要為所有世界出現既不公平而發聲"},{"pid":"3a4394f2494309a85f893cf03df79fbc9b79ee0b","tid":1481621,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:51:44.000Z","msg":"報恩啊！"},{"pid":"1b762179984bd2bdf278d7cc0761c716dadadbf3","tid":1481621,"uid":27008,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:52:54.000Z","msg":"旅行救國<br />\n就係同唔同國家既人互舉旗幟<br />\n著黑衫帶眼罩豬嘴黃頭盔<br />\n試想下如果可以集郵集到幾十張唔同國家既人舉你支旗既相<br />\n畫面係幾咁鼓舞 而唔係剩係得把聲"},{"pid":"cac18a5625c7c45696e5b597af327f60e36bd434","tid":1481621,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:53:28.000Z","msg":"當全世界幫緊我地個陣 先有希望對抗 <br />\n希望之後我地可以幫返其他人"},{"pid":"c9f6050a605dc17a54bfff3c642fc9483f4dae06","tid":1481621,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:53:39.000Z","msg":"包唔包括中國<br />\n建設民主中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893f10f79536fa3fa396d828938497a9505e2ba2","tid":1481621,"uid":20584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b762179984bd2bdf278d7cc0761c716dadadbf3","tid":1481621,"uid":27008,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:52:54.000Z","msg":"旅行救國<br />\n就係同唔同國家既人互舉旗幟<br />\n著黑衫帶眼罩豬嘴黃頭盔<br />\n試想下如果可以集郵集到幾十張唔同國家既人舉你支旗既相<br />\n畫面係幾咁鼓舞 而唔係剩係得把聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:54:31.000Z","msg":"好似法國之後黎緊既遊行 我地都可以聲援佢地"},{"pid":"ae7a0c2bddadd82154561b8273768c8723412b93","tid":1481621,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9f6050a605dc17a54bfff3c642fc9483f4dae06","tid":1481621,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:53:39.000Z","msg":"包唔包括中國<br />\n建設民主中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:54:49.000Z","msg":"你就收皮啦 波台狗"},{"pid":"d009768c42e982bff2dae412fe100a87b4f53293","tid":1481621,"uid":276779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:54:59.000Z","msg":"台灣係太陽花 茉莉花係埃及"},{"pid":"0029311fdddb3851c920c03b1b215c1888f7c102","tid":1481621,"uid":268251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:56:29.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNrEn9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNrEn9y.jpg&h=3a63f7b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1481244/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1481244/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原圖既少女, 係孤星淚入面既Cosette. 孤星淚係咩故事, 大家應該都知, 唔知自己google.<br />\n留意左好多文日, 我地既文宣其實可以利用唔同地方既文化,<br />\n加以更改, 達成更大效果. 要同全世界We Connect, 要活用唔同地方既文化.<br />\n孤星淚, 係歐美社會一定知道既title, 亦容易勾起佢地既共鳴.<br />\n大家不妨諗諗之後既文宣, 要更加creative.<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫手forward去外國網站或者FB,<br />\n喺澳洲同法國既香港支持者受到大陸人攻擊之下,<br />\n呢張圖就係我地對外文宣既最佳利器.<br />\n當年南斯拉夫內戰, 打左幾年, 國際社會關注但唔出手,<br />\n最後係一張『薩拉熱窩的羅密歐與茱麗葉』既照片成為轉變關鍵.<br />\n羅密歐與茱麗葉既標題, 引起左歐美社會共鳴.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n接下來係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">理念輸出</span></span><br />\n[文宣] 發夢之歌: 自由之旗・自由之民, 一首代表我地理念既歌.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1476260/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1476260/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我地唔單止要宣傳, 仲要有理念. 藉由歌聲追求自由係最好既理念文宣,<br />\n唔會嚇親老一派既香港人, 亦可以觸動到歐美社會既支持.<br />\n我選呢首歌既理由, 同上面講既『薩拉熱窩的羅密歐與茱麗葉』一樣,<br />\n都係能觸動歐美普世價值既issue. 對我地黎講, 一首好歌,<br />\n可以鼓舞士氣, 提醒我地不要放棄.<br />\n<br />\n上面條LINK係我搵既一首歌, 好適合我地用. 大家可以襟上去聽下首歌,<br />\n如果認同既話, 我希望可以搞個萬人齊唱版, 大家可以聽住音樂清唱,<br />\n唱完之後UPLOAD上上面條連登LINK, 我整合之後放出黎.<br />\n<br />\n文宣也好, 歌曲也好, 最重要係做得到be Symbol.<br />\nBatman曾有一段對話:<br />\n&ldquo;People need dramatic examples to shake them out of apathy,<br />\nand I can&rsquo;t do that as Bruce Wayne. As a man I&rsquo;m flesh and blood,<br />\nI can be ignored, I can be destroyed, but as a symbol,<br />\nas a symbol I can be incorruptible. I can be everlasting.&rdquo;<br />\n&mdash; Bruce Wayne (Batman Begins)<br />\n<br />\n我地既文宣同理念, 一定要做到be Symbol, 一聽到某D文宣圖就諗起成個運動,<br />\n一聽到某首歌就能夠代表我地. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">be Symbol, be Symbol, be Symbol</span></span>.<br />\n重要事情講三次.<br />\n<br />\n唯有有左Symbol, 有左令我地寄托夢想既Symbol, 先可以長期落去.<br />\n我地無大台, 唔似印度人有甘地去寄托夢想, 寄托夢想於歌曲就係最好選擇.<br />\n<br />\n818，維園見"},{"pid":"16c5cc74c60d84eebec450ba041a0b9d110e60be","tid":1481621,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d009768c42e982bff2dae412fe100a87b4f53293","tid":1481621,"uid":276779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:54:59.000Z","msg":"台灣係太陽花 茉莉花係埃及"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌 柒左 亂左添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e31db8efc88989860c21bed94af30dfb8427a2","tid":1481621,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:57:03.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"b65f519f9d0b2aa458ec1712010f1b5c9f2a927b","tid":1481621,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"893f10f79536fa3fa396d828938497a9505e2ba2"